					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9118864#post-4109593</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9118864/scp-4047#post-4109593</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 05 Jan 2019 19:40:16 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Crow-Cat</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3952131</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>SCP-4047 was discovered by Agent ████████ Miller reported numerous anomalous disturbances in the staff and student population of ████████ Secondary School</p> </blockquote> <p>This sentence is strangely worded. Perhaps &quot;by&quot; should be &quot;when?&quot;</p> <blockquote> <p>Additionally SCP-4047-A and numerous instances SCP-4047-B physically and anomalously assaulted the initial recovery team. SCP-4047-B instances were considered acceptable casualties and SCP-4047-A was successfully recovered</p> </blockquote> <p>When referring to SCP-4047-A, it reads like it's meant to refer to SCP-4047. Is this a typo?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
