				<wikidot:authorName>Edna Granbo</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2212713</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>You should use the scientific name in the article and have the common name in the footnotes.</p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-4047's physical and psychological health is to be monitored and recorded</p> </blockquote> <p>Should be are not is.</p> <blockquote> <p>Changes in SCP-4047's health or behaviour are to tracked</p> </blockquote> <p>Should be is not are.</p> <p>Other than those small mistakes I really like this. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
